beer.beer_description: Old Bounder, an homage to yesteryear's ales, is an intense, barrel-aged barleywine. Hints of stonefruit and woody undertones are complemented by smooth caramel sweetness, bold hop character, and a warming alcohol content. Perfect for post-dinner indulgence or dessert pairing, Old Bounder is crafted for connoisseurs seeking the finest, embodying a voyage into bold flavors.

items.badge_description: Cheers, beer patriot! You are supporting the small and independent American craft brewer. When you see the seal -- shaped like an upside-down beer bottle -- that's independence you're tasting. Try 5 more to earn Level 59!

You don't always intend to go for beers with a double digit ABV, but when you do, you make it count! Cheers to you, but be careful, 10% and up can really pack a punch. That's 185 different beers with an ABV of 10% and up. Try 5 more for Level 38!
